{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341710/extras/veranMightHoriz.gif?t=1736741241\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> CTT is a fast paced roguelite platformer focused on action rather than platforming, featuring handcrafted levels. Fight your way through hordes of enemies using powerful spells, potent skills, permanent upgrades and lots of bullets. Discover the secrets of Anarth, explore intriguing landscapes and face terrible foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341710/extras/Handcrafted_Levels.png?t=1736741241\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Levels are handmade and selected from a large pool. Each one has a unique layout, different secrets and unique items, guaranteeing a very unique run every time you die. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341710/extras/steamGIFLevelVersions.gif?t=1736741241\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341710/extras/TextsTemplate.png?t=1736741241\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Death is a learning experience! Upon dying you can permanently upgrade different skills and face the challenge again, stronger. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341710/extras/Spells.png?t=1736741241\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will come across powerful spells to help you along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every spell you acquire will always be at the tips of your fingers. You can switch and use them at your pleasure and wreak havoc among your enemies. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341710/extras/Passive_Upgrades.png?t=1736741241\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As well as spells, you will equip passive upgrades to increase your chances of success. Improve your bullets and skills as well as many other perks. You can equip up to 6 upgrades at any given time, swapping them and combining them as you like to find the most optimal or most fun way to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341710/extras/BossesMiniBossesAndMore.png?t=1736741241\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you go through each run you'll might run into a thought boss, different random mini bosses and other unique challenges that will test your resolve.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Sentinel Defeated","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/11e810c43b00ddfd01336b2b484288478b72bfab.jpg"},{"name":"Near Death Victory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/4c41d22607b429673f346885215d38d0c8fc852a.jpg"},{"name":"The Untouchable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/c98c7f0e4cb799d02fafd10f1a6a1ba8145d651b.jpg"},{"name":"Enemy of Turrets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/24a79b010644b5ff3025d1e15f6d087e84cabb05.jpg"},{"name":"Mastery","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/ca76582618740d9c47125bdf67499633cc1fe712.jpg"},{"name":"Troll Vanquisher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/c01e644617dec097a1c7378ef99cf842f3a3df95.jpg"},{"name":"Perseverance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/7d0bb28ea9802a4ccc4d4a4ca1ca690307b8475d.jpg"},{"name":"Red Commander","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2341710/41e128ac77595e545b5a9d